      1972 data retrieved from World Health Organization. (‚Äé1974)‚Äé. Weekly Epidemiological Record, 1974, vol. 49, 2 [‚Äéfull issue]‚Äé. Weekly Epidemiological Record = Relev√© √©pid√©miologique hebdomadaire, 49 (‚Äé2)‚Äé, 9-24. http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/handle/10665/219695/WER4902.PDF?sequence=1&isAllowed=y
