      1976 data retrieved from World Health Organization. (‚Äé1977)‚Äé. Weekly Epidemiological Record, 1977, vol. 52, 2 [‚Äéfull issue]‚Äé. Weekly Epidemiological Record = Relev√© √©pid√©miologique hebdomadaire, 52 (‚Äé2)‚Äé, 9-20. http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/handle/10665/221189/WER5202.PDF?sequence=1&isAllowed=y
